                        <div class="item">
                            <div class="opener-wrapper">
                                <h3><a class="opener" href="#">BCCS COVID-19 Emergency Relief Fund </a></h3>
                                <strong class="subtitle"></strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide">
                                <p>We know that impact of COVID-19 has been tremendous on many.  That is why we have set up the <strong>BCCS COVID-19 Emergency Relief Fund</strong> to provide financial support to families and alumni of our community who are facing extreme financial hardship.</p>
<p><strong><em>Make a Gift of Any Amount Today</em></strong><br>
Your 100% tax-deductible contribution can be made directly on our website <a href="https://www.bostoncollegiate.org/donate/"><strong>here</strong></a>.  Gifts of any amount are much appreciated and will be directly put into the hands of BCCS families and alumni to help meet their basic needs.</p>
<p>Additionally, fo<em><strong>r the duration of the school closure, a generous BCCS supported has pledged to donate $1,000 each week to our Emergency Relief Fund if the BCCS community can collectively match the same amount.</strong></em>  Help us meet this challenge!</p>
<p><em><strong>Apply for Support<br></strong></em>If you are a BCCS family or alumnus seeking financial support from the Fund, please complete <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeSQoXG9khlg-CNfg5X5Ighnw80kReTAX0Py2s2_-EbSbGLAw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1"><strong>this form</strong></a>.  If you have questions or need any assistance completing the form, please contact Teresa Rodriguez, Director of Family and Community Relations, at <a href="mailto:trodriguez@bostoncollegiate.org">trodriguez@bostoncollegiate.org</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
